GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
H 1
HOUSE BILL 1118
Short Title: Workforce Housing Loan Renewal Act. (Public)
Sponsors: Representatives Chesser, Schietzelt, Willingham, and Buansi (Primary
Sponsors).
For a complete list of sponsors, refer to the North Carolina General Assembly web site.
Referred to: Appropriations, if favorable, Rules, Calendar, and Operations of the House
April 30, 2026
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE RECURRING FUNDS TO THE WORKFORCE HOUSING
3 LOAN PROGRAM.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Housing Finance
6 Agency the sum of thirty-five million dollars ($35,000,000) in recurring funds beginning with
7 the 2026-2027 fiscal year to be used for the Workforce Housing Loan Program.
8 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
